<LI>P. Degano, J.-V. Loddo and C. Priami. <I>Mobile
Processes with Local Clocks</I>. In Proceedings of Workshop on Analysis
and Verification of Multiple-Agent Languages, Stockholm 1996.
<a href="files/degano-loddo-priami--mobile-processes--1996.ps.gz">ps.gz</a></LI>

